I wonder what aspects of the Dalai Lama's real teachings can be adapted here. Compassion, interconnectedness, mindfulness, and letting go are central. But in this fantasy context, they can be presented as mystical truths from another dimension. So, perhaps each lesson can have a name that reflects both the teaching and the mystical element.


